      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/><strong>RenderManStudio_Assembly_v01.hip</strong><br/><br/>This scene contains all the studio assets in a default layout, ready for you to create your own scene.  Feel free to explore through the <em>stagemanager </em>to see all the fun model and shading variants that live with the USD assets. <br/><br/>Included in the scene is a camera and a number of lights which will give you the render you see below.  <br/><br/>The <em>usd_Assembly</em> USD rop node exists to save out this default layout to <em>$HIP/usd/Assembly/RenderManStudio_Assembly_v01.usda - </em>which is referenced by RenderManStudio_Layout_v01.hip<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642618/RenderMan_Solaris_RenderManStudio_BaseScene.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642618/RenderMan_Solaris_RenderManStudio_BaseScene.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642638\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_RenderManStudio_BaseScene.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642618\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"efa4adea-9ef5-41c6-82ae-9b6e7ecd0986\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManStudio_Assembly_ScreenShot_Solaris.JPG\" width=\"404\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642618/RenderManStudio_Assembly_ScreenShot_Solaris.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=404&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642618/RenderManStudio_Assembly_ScreenShot_Solaris.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1021\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642635\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Assembly_ScreenShot_Solaris.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642618\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7ac36cdb-af05-477e-892a-edddca91a0ae\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642618/RenderManStudio_Assembly_ScreenShot_Solaris.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=808&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642618/RenderManStudio_Assembly_ScreenShot_Solaris.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=404&amp;height=214 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManStudio_Assembly_Solaris.jpg\" width=\"377\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642618/RenderManStudio_Assembly_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=377&amp;height=215\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642618/RenderManStudio_Assembly_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1095\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642632\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Assembly_Solaris.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642618\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a1204b10-58d8-41ee-8e64-c5d122738dbd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642618/RenderManStudio_Assembly_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=754&amp;height=430 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642618/RenderManStudio_Assembly_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=377&amp;height=215 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"embeddedObject conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"f392687e-11e2-462f-bdb4-d1336db099de\" data-macro-id=\"653e051c-93b5-43ee-80c2-9ceae4b8a766\" data-macro-name=\"multimedia\">\n    <video src=\"/wiki/download/attachments/544642618/HardCase_Turntable.mp4\" height=\"380\" width=\"890\" autoplay=\"\" controls=\"\">\n        Your browser does not support the HTML5 video element\n</video>\n\n</div><p><br/><br/>Feel free to add your own assets to the stage manager and then you can then move on to the next stage, <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/display/RFH25/Layout+Stage\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shot Layout</a><br/><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
